<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de" xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <title>Dein Anmeldelink</title>
  <!--[if mso]>
  <noscript>
    <xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch></o:OfficeDocumentSettings></xml>
  </noscript>
  <![endif]-->
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor="#f4f4f4">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 32px 16px;">

        <!-- Card -->
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="max-width: 600px; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 32px 40px;">

              <!-- Heading -->
              <h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">
                Hallo {{firstName}},
              </h1>

              <!-- Body text -->
              <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #444444;">
                Du hast eine Anmeldung für ChorHub angefordert. Du hast zwei Möglichkeiten, dich anzumelden:
              </p>

              <!-- Option 1: Magic Link box -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse; border-color: #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px;">

                    <p style="margin: 0 0 4px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">
                      Option 1 – Anmeldelink
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #666666;">
                      Funktioniert im Browser · Dauerhaft gültig
                    </p>

                    <!-- Bulletproof button -->
                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td align="center">
                          <!--[if mso]>
                          <v:roundrect xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word"
                            href="{{magicUrl}}" style="height:50px;v-text-anchor:middle;width:200px;" arcsize="16%" fillcolor="#006FEE" strokecolor="#006FEE">
                            <w:anchorlock/>
                            <center style="color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;">Jetzt anmelden</center>
                          </v:roundrect>
                          <![endif]-->
                          <!--[if !mso]><!-->
                          <a href="{{magicUrl}}" target="_blank"
                             style="background-color: #006FEE; color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                                    font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; padding: 16px 36px;
                                    text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; mso-hide: all;">
                            Jetzt anmelden
                          </a>
                          <!--<![endif]-->
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>

                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Option 2: Login code box -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse; border-color: #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px;">

                    <p style="margin: 0 0 4px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">
                      Option 2 – Einmalcode
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #666666;">
                      Gilt nur 15 Minuten
                    </p>

                    <!-- Code display -->
                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td align="center" bgcolor="#f4f4f4" style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
                          <span style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 40px; font-weight: bold;
                                       letter-spacing: 10px; color: #1a1a1a; display: block;">
                            {{loginCode}}
                          </span>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>

                    <p style="margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666666;">
                      Öffne die ChorHub-App, gib deine E-Mail-Adresse ein, und trag dann diesen Code ein.
                    </p>

                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Footer note -->
              <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #888888;">
                Falls du diese E-Mail nicht angefordert hast, kannst du sie ignorieren.
              </p>

              <!-- Divider -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                <tr>
                  <td style="border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; padding-top: 24px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #aaaaaa;">
                      ChorHub – Chororganisation
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <!-- /Card -->

      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
